tagDescription: In memoriam scrapbooks - Letters and Telegrams of condolence and newspaper clippings on the occasion of Clifford Sifton's death.

Alverstone - Copy of the memorandum "What channel is the Portland channel?" This is the original opinion of Baron Alverstone, which on account of international complications was withdrawn and never published. Accompanying this Copy is a 1942 sworn deposition of Miss Margery Wade, daughter of F. C. Wade.
Family Record - scrapbooks containing Correspondence, notes and memorabilia Concerning the compiling of a genealogical record of the Sifton family.
